OL,3,CUS driver jailed after head-on crash
OL,4,Cwhich left nurse unable to walk
OL,6,FA US citizen who left the country
OL,7,Fafter leaving a mental health nurse
OL,8,Ftemporarily paralysed has been jailed
OL,9,Fafter he was extradited.
OL,11,FIsaac Calderon, who was 22 at the time
OL,12,Fof the incident and is now 23, was
OL,13,Fsentenced on 7 November to 32 months
OL,14,Fin prison for causing serious injury
OL,15,Fby dangerous driving at Worcester
OL,16,FCrown Court.
OL,18,FHe appeared by video link to HMP
OL,19,FHewell.
