OL,3,CUS driver jailed after head-on crash
OL,4,Cwhich left nurse unable to walk
OL,6,FIn July 2023, nurse Elizabeth Donowho,
OL,7,Ffrom Malvern, suffered life changing
OL,8,Finjuries after he crashed into her,
OL,9,Flosing control of his Honda Accord car.
OL,11,FShe suffered multiple fractures in the
OL,12,Fcrash, including breaks in both
OL,13,Fankles, her right hand and sternum and
OL,14,Fwas left unable to walk for six weeks.
OL,16,FMs Donowho, was a freelance nurse on
OL,17,Fher way home from working at a
OL,18,Fhospital in unit in Hereford.
