OL,3,CUS driver jailed after head-on crash
OL,4,Cwhich left nurse unable to walk
OL,6,FCalderon crashed into the 57 year
OL,7,Fold's Mercedes on the A14103 in
OL,8,FShucknall, Herefordshire.
OL,10,FDashcam footage played inside court
OL,11,Fshowed Calderon crashing head on into
OL,12,FMs Donowho's car after he decided to
OL,13,Fovertake her at high speed.
OL,15,FAfter the incident, Calderon avoided
OL,16,Fjustice by heading back to the US.
OL,18,FHe left the UK on a commercial flight
OL,19,Fto Texas on 25 November ahead of a
OL,20,Fscheduled UK court hearing.
