OL,6,FPolice then issued a warrant for his
OL,7,Farrest in December last year.
OL,9,FCalderon pleaded guilty to the
OL,10,Foffences last July.
OL,12,FThe judge commented that a week before
OL,13,Fthe accident, Calderon bought the car
OL,14,Fand was driving it uninsured.
OL,16,FHe said: "It was the sort of driving
OL,17,Fone expects from arrogant young boy
OL,18,Fracers.
