OL,6,FThe 23-year-old was also given a two
OL,7,Fyear ban for his offences which he
OL,8,Fwill serve after his release.
OL,10,FIn a statement following the
OL,11,Fsentencing hearing, the Senior Crown
OL,12,FProsecutor for CPS West Midlands said:
OL,13,F"We worked closely with the US
OL,14,Fauthorities to make sure our
OL,15,Fextradition request progressed swiftly
OL,16,Fso that Calderon was brought back to
OL,17,Fthe UK to face the consequences of his
OL,18,Factions.
