OL,6,FA spokeperson for Elizabeth, Radd
OL,7,FSeiger said, "Following the sentencing
OL,8,Fof Isaac Calderon today, Elizabeth is
OL,9,Fhugely relieved that her campaign for
OL,10,Fjustice has succeeded and that Mr
OL,11,FCalderon has at long last been held
OL,12,Faccountable for his terrible actions
OL,13,Fand dangerous driving which led to the
OL,14,Fcrash."
